    </section>

    <section class="fade-in-section">
        <div class="section-title">The Coffee Identity Movement</div>
        <p>Coffee in the U.S. has evolved into a personal ritual, a cultural icon, and a shared experience. Every cup—whether brewed at home, ordered at a café, or given as a gift—tells a story.</p>
        <p>It’s a story of identity, connection, and meaning, reflecting who we are, how we see ourselves, and how we share our lives, one cup at a time.</p>
        <p>Tomorrow morning, when you craft your perfect brew, remember: You’re not just drinking coffee, you’re participating in a cultural ritual as personal as it is universal.</p>
    </section>
</div>

